messages.message: :alarm: *NEW CHANNEL ALERT! //* <#C0547G8P0F5|> is live! This is a new communication channel for publicizing technical design docs and getting reviews from engineers across the company. The goal of this channel is to help you stay in the loop on new features and projects across EPD. Please keep in mind our Slack Comm Guidelines (https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1uGYZdpBetyiVteeXRcKnohR4015PQuR75SZmoHhz9tU/edit#slide=id.ga935040ac4_0_116), and thread on posts when possible! Looking forward to having more visibility across the org! :meow_code:
